To Make:
	make

To Clean:
	make clean

Descriptions:
	player: independent player, plays local files
	nutella: the server and client executable, mode depends on flag (-c for client, -s for server)

To Run Client:
	./nutella -c

To Run Server:
	./nutella -s

To Run Player:
	./player [file]

Note:
	Nutella server will use the directory stored in $NUTELLA for the path to movies,
	it will non recursively search when query comes in.
